

**Matsh pi e edagi g Jesus hon cheho ch ed **

*An g neid g Matthew 28:1-8; Mark 16:1-8; Luke 24:1-12 *

1 Domig wabsh i siꞌalim mad wabsh kia s‑chuhugam, tsh gm hu hihi hegam Mary Magdalene k am dada cheo t am. Kutsh heki hu gam hu i e nuꞌichkwua g hodai mad hekaj ab chum kuhpi. 2 Tsh am chum neid k am hahawa uhpam meh kihhim wui k ad gd hu t‑wui mel ahni John ch Simon Peter k am t‑ahgid ch hab kaij, “Am atki i e wuhshad g t‑kownaligbad hon heg amjed hihaꞌini mat am e cheh. Kuch pi shaꞌi mahch mas hebai has e juh.” 

3 Kuchd g Peter wehm am ha hekaj wohp. 4 Nid ahni wehpeg ged hu mel nanid pi ahni baꞌich i s‑hohtam meh mad g Peter. 5 Nid am i koachsh k nei mo am wehch hegai s‑kehg ikus k wabshaba pi am hu i wah. 6 D am hahawa mel g Peter k am wabsh si i wah k cheh hegai ikus 7 ch heg ehp mat hekaj e hobino g Jesus moꞌo. D id ged hu hab wabsh hejelko holiwek ch kahch. 8 Kunid ahni am hahawa epai i wah k am i neidok ab hahawa i s‑wohoch mat woho i wuhsh ab muhkig amjed. 9 Kuchd eda pi koi s‑amichud hegai Jiosh oꞌohana mo hab chuꞌig mat hemho wa wo i wuhsh ab muhkig amjed. 10 Kuchd gam hu hahawa hihi uhpam. 

**Matsh g Jesus am i e chehgi Mary Magdalene wui **

*An g neid g Matthew 28:9-10; Mark 16:9-11 *

11 Sh am ep oimmed g Mary cheo kihjego ch shoak ch atsh am i e jumalkad k am i koachsh hihaꞌini ch ed 12 ch ash gohk ha neid g anghil. Idam ash s‑tohtam e enigadadch ch ga hu aꞌai dadha, hema ab moꞌoshko ch hema ga hu aigo 13 ch hab kaij, “Uwi, shahchu ap ahgch shoak?” 

Sh hab kaij ab ha wui, “Heg hekaj matki gam hu i e bei g ni‑kownalig muhki. Kuni pi mahch mas hebai e cheh.” 14 Tsh hab cheꞌiok ab sikol i kekiwua k ash neid mash ab hema kehk ch ash wabshaba pi shaꞌi mahch mo hedai wud. 

15 Sh eda d Jesus ch ab kakke ch hab kaij, “Uwi shahchu ap ahgch shoak? Dohp in gahg?” 

Kush hab e ahg mo d eꞌes nuhkuddam ch hab kaij ab wui, “Ab g si s‑ni‑hoꞌigeꞌid k am ni‑ahgid mapt hebai hab cheh. Nt am wo him k am wo bei.” 

16 Sh hab kaij g Jesus ab wui, “Mary.” 

Tsh ab hahawa ep i neid k hab kaij e‑neꞌoki ed, “Raboni\!” mo hab d ahga “Ni‑mashchamdam\!” 

17 Sh hab kaij g Jesus, “Pi g am hu ni‑shohbid. Koi ant am hu hih ni‑ohg wui. Pt wabshaba am wo him k am wo ha ahgi g ni‑naipijju mant wo uhpam i ni‑nodagi heg wui mo d ni‑ohg ch ahpim d ep em‑ohg. Heg o d ni‑Jioshga ch ahpim d ep em‑Jioshga.” 

18 D wa woho am uhpam hih g Mary Magdalene k am t‑ahgi mo neid g t‑kownalig Jesus. K heg am ahgid ihda. 

**Matsh g Jesus am i e chehgi e‑chuhchai ha wui **

*An g neid g Matthew 28:16-20; Mark 16:14-18; Luke 24:36-49 *

19 D gam hu si i juh domig hudunk. Kuchd am t‑nam hema kih am. D ga hu si yahwidag g kihkjeg nachd pi s‑ha ehbid g hahaꞌichu. 

D wabshaba am haha wabsh jiwia g Jesus t‑wui k hab kaij, “Am g wabsh wo s‑ap e tahtk,” 20 ch ab hahawa t‑chehgid g e‑nohnhoi ch e‑huda. Kuchd si s‑hehgig ab i neidok. 

21 D hab ep kaij ab t‑wui, “Am g wabsh wo s‑ap e tahtk. Am ant i em‑chuhcha hab masma mat g ni‑ohg am i ni‑kei. Kumt hab waꞌap am wo ahgachugad g haꞌichu ahgaj.” 22 T hab chei ihda k ab t‑dahm ihbheiwua k hab kaij, “Ab g wo i behꞌi g Hekia S‑apꞌekam Gewkdag. 23 Kumt wo s‑mahch k ah mas hedai g pi ap chuꞌijigaj gm hu hab i juni g Jiosh ch hedai pi gam hu hab i juni.” Neh, bad kaij ch am hahawa i piꞌata. 

**Mash g Thomas chum pi wohochud mat uhpam i wuhsh g Jesus **

24 D g Thomas pi am hu t‑wehmaj mad wa am jiwia g Jesus. 25 Kuchd am hahawa chum ahgid matt nei g t‑kownalig. 

D hab kaij g Thomas, “Bant waꞌi masma wo s‑wohoch mat uhpam i wuhsh mant wo nei g nohnhoij mat ab wo s‑babaliwanik mamt ab sisish k ab wo taht abai k ab ep wo taht hudaj ab.” 

26 Hemako domig amjed, chd am ep i t‑hemapai kih ch ed. D am hahawa t‑wehmaj g Thomas. Chd ab ep si yahwidadch g kihkjeg. D wabshaba ab i wah g Jesus k am jiwia t‑wui k hab kaij, “Am g wabsh wo si s‑ap e tahtk.” 27 D hab hahawa kaij ab Thomas wui, “Ab g i ni‑neid k ab tahtam g ni‑nohnhoi ch ni‑huda k ab wo s‑ni‑wohochudad.” 

28 D hab hahawa chei g Thomas, “Ni‑kownalig ch ni‑Jioshga\!” 

29 D hab ep kaij g Jesus ab wui, “Ab apt i s‑ni‑wohoch nap pi ni‑neid. Baꞌich at wo i s‑hehgigk hegam mat ab wo i s‑ni‑wohoch wa chum pi g e‑wuhpuikaj ni‑neidch.” 

**Matsh haschu ahgk e oꞌoha ihda oꞌohana **

30 Muꞌi s‑hasig haꞌichu ad hab ep juh g Jesus am t‑nena ed mant pi oꞌoha id eda oꞌohana. 31 Nt id in hi wa ha oꞌoha mamt ab amjed wo s‑wohoch mo g Jesus d Jiosh si Kehsha ch d alidaj k hab masma ab wo bei g wechij doakag. 

